{"type":"question","id":17750,"title":"【开脑洞】中南海龙椅与煤山歪脖树之间是否只有一场天灾的距离？","uid":16211,"topics":[1,2497,5037],"contents":"文昭老师的节目中讲过，加速明朝灭亡的主要有四个因素，即<b>瘟疫、民变、中央集权削弱和天灾。</b><br>\n<br>\n结合目前的局势<br>\n<br>\n瘟疫有了✅<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/yq6dHRJ.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yq6dHRJ.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/yq6dHRJ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n民变的基础，包括身处内地的葱油、被镇压的反抗者、甚至香港的抗争者也有了，只差出来牵头的“李自成”了✅<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/hNAtngU.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hNAtngU.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/hNAtngU.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/U4D3Elm.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/U4D3Elm.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/U4D3Elm.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n中央集权削弱的迹象也有了，各地自保军阀割据的景象已现✅<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/kBIBH1W.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kBIBH1W.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/kBIBH1W.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n天灾❌<br>\n似乎离包帝吊死煤山歪脖树就差一场大的天灾了，当年崇祯帝还有太监王承恩陪死，不知道王沪宁王岐山二位王公公是否愿意陪着包帝一起走。<br>\n<br>\n大家怎么看？","date":"2020-02-08","agreeCount":3,"discussionCount":2}